  Registration is on a site basis.  One registration entitles use of the code
by one programmer or one office.  Companies or agencies that use these
libraries or code in developing software at multiple sites must have one
registered copy per site.  Prices are in roubles for poor guys struggling for
life in USSR, or in US dollars for guys living in shining west. Prices in
roubles may change in the future because the value of rouble drops fast...

